<title>
Transaxle Left Case Disassembly and Reassembly
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B5206010">Manual Transaxle Unit Dismounting and Remounting</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B5206013">Manual Transaxle Assembly Components</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B5206017001">
<title>
Disassembly
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove oil gutter (1) if necessary.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B520018.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "46.471mm" ver = "01" gw = "171" gh = "115"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B5206017002">
<title>
Reassembly
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install oil gutter (1) if removed.
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Be sure to use new oil gutter bolt with pre-coated adhesive. Otherwise, bolt may loosen.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
<torque>
<torqueitem id = "T5B020">
<t-part>
Oil gutter bolt
</t-part>
<t-part1>
a
</t-part1>
<t-value1>
10
</t-value1>
<t-value2>
1.0
</t-value2>
<t-value3>
7.5
</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B520021.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "49.091mm" ver = "01" gw = "171" gh = "123"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
